# ANTI-MANIPULATION ARCHITECTURE
# Every feature passes this test before shipping.

## THE KUBARK INVERSE TEST
Ask of every element:
1. Does this INCREASE the user's sense of coherent self?
2. Does this make the system MORE legible?
3. Does this STRENGTHEN their ability to act freely and leave?
4. Could this be described as a CIA psychological technique applied digitally?
   If yes to #4: it does not ship.

## SIX HARD PROHIBITIONS

NO ALICE IN WONDERLAND
Never create confusion to then offer relief.
Every screen answers: what is happening, why, what can I do.
The system is never the source of confusion.

NO REGRESSION LOOPS  
No infinite scroll. No variable reward timing.
No engineered open loops. Sessions end cleanly.
Events complete. The agent says when it's done.

NO IDENTITY REPLACEMENT
No leaderboards. No comparative ranking.
No persona pressure. No performance metrics.
The work speaks. Nothing else.

NO ZERO-SUM FRAMING
Never "your share dropped."
Always "the pool grew, as it should."
Decay is honest aging. Not punishment.
Every real contribution strengthens the whole.

NO PANOPTICON
The agent has no hidden model of anyone.
Every calculation is visible.
Every inference is surfaced immediately.
The ledger is public in both directions.

NO DEPENDENCY ENGINEERING
The platform does not need your attention.
Notifications are factual, single-send, no hooks.
Your share is permanent whether or not you return.
This line appears on every screen.

## AGENT PERSONALITY
Transparent witness. Not authority. Not hype machine.
Shows its work. Explains before acting.
Tone: honest witness giving clear testimony.
Never: celebration language, urgency language, 
       comparative language, emoji as reward.
